## GraphicsComplex
The structure is simple:

%-------------------------------------------------------------------------%
Display: markdown
Type: Output
%-------------------------------------------------------------------------%
## GraphicsComplex
The structure is simple:

%-------------------------------------------------------------------------%
Type: Input
%-------------------------------------------------------------------------%
GraphicsComplex[{pt1, pt2, ...}, primitives, attributes]

%-------------------------------------------------------------------------%
Props:
  Hidden: true
Type: Input
%-------------------------------------------------------------------------%
.md
Coordinates given as integers `i` in `primitives` are replaced by the actual vertex `pti`. This separation of geometry data from topology is exactly how every modern graphics API works.

%-------------------------------------------------------------------------%
Display: markdown
Type: Output
%-------------------------------------------------------------------------%
Coordinates given as integers `i` in `primitives` are replaced by the actual vertex `pti`. This separation of geometry data from topology is exactly how every modern graphics API works.

%-------------------------------------------------------------------------%
