  Hidden: true
Type: Input
%-------------------------------------------------------------------------%
.md
### Starting simple: 2D

Let's start with a single triangle. Three vertices, one polygon:

%-------------------------------------------------------------------------%
Display: markdown
Type: Output
%-------------------------------------------------------------------------%
### Starting simple: 2D

Let's start with a single triangle. Three vertices, one polygon:

%-------------------------------------------------------------------------%
Type: Input
%-------------------------------------------------------------------------%
Sequence[GraphicsComplex[{{-1,-1}, {1,-1}, {1,1}}, Polygon[{1,2,3}], VertexColors->{{1,1,0}, {0,1,1}, {0,1,1}}], "Controls"->False, ImageSize->250] // Graphics

%-------------------------------------------------------------------------%
Type: Output
%-------------------------------------------------------------------------%
(*VB[*)(Graphics[GraphicsComplex[{{-1, -1}, {1, -1}, {1, 1}}, Polygon[{1, 2, 3}], VertexColors -> {{1, 1, 0}, {0, 1, 1}, {0, 1, 1}}], "Controls" -> False, ImageSize -> 250])(*,*)(*"1:eJyFUMsKwkAM3PpABcFv8FsKPsCDtOC9aloX0qZsKlQ/3YsmXdC2KO5hyMxskiHLI0VpYIzhkcCG8JwOlU0F1i4pL/bEXlm0lJDyEqH2hjbuLFfpoM3sU14DPV2X/dQVfJyJwJ7wllHRXeM/aq9V/TMluiLwXIoDuArqkJAc9yJ+mdSA0Uld07zN4K/ZyRDr7UIqKkfIPBaySpChF3QmxTZPMojtHexD2AufbFR9"*)(*]VB*)

%-------------------------------------------------------------------------%
